setAcknowledged

public void setAcknowledged(boolean ack)
setAcknowledged - sets boolean indicating whether alert has been acknowleged BOZO - Definition of 'acknowledged' is fuzzy. I assume that an alert which requires an operator response can not acknowledged without the response. I see no code enforcing this behaviour.
